4. The number of food-borne violations
It looks like the count number is within an element with class ‚ÄúinspectionCountNumber‚Äù. BUT: this class is repeated on the retail violations element as well as the food-borne violations element. So, we‚Äôll need to use nested selectors
First, select elements with the ‚ÄúinspectionUnitCountFoodborne‚Äù class name and then the ‚ÄúinspectionCountNumber‚Äù class name.


